description: Photoshop Album stores PSA files in "C:\Documents and Settings\All Users\Application Data\Adobe\Photoshop Album\Catalogs."
The Photoshop Elements 3.0 Organizer stores PSA files in "C:\Documents and Settings\All Users\Application Data\Adobe\Catalogs."
NOTE: PSA files were used up through Photoshop Elements 5.0. They can be converted to the newer file format in versions 6.0 and 7.0.
